Welcome to the very first (but definitely not last) collaboration map between the members of CW community. This map has 9 small to average size levels. Credits:
level 1 - jake
level 2 - flume
level 3 - turk
level 4 - sk
levle 5 - kalipso
level 6 - mellowed
level 7 - recky
level 8 - serz
level 9 - george
Stay tuned for future collab maps. Also, big thanks to serz for putting the parts together and making a working map <3 and thanks to Turk for organizing this whole collab idea.
